{
  "texts": [
    "Similarly, while Malandri et al. (2023) focuses on answering user questions in their dialogues, their main goal is to clarify the ML model for users.",
    "In a collaborative scenario involving a human and a robot, Sklar and Azhar (2018) center their dialogue on jointly planning the next steps.",
    "Notably, the end of these dialogues is not necessarily marked by user comprehension, but often by user disengagement.",
    "Overall, while different systems implement single components of the suggested properties, there are a few properties that are poorly addressed in our analyzed studies.",
    "No system implements an explainer that can question the explainee's request."
  ]
}